## ğŸ¨ Design System

The project uses a comprehensive design token system with responsive breakpoints:

- **Colors**: Blue primary palette with complementary seafoam and sand tones
- **Typography**: Inter font with responsive sizing (desktop â†’ mobile)
- **Spacing**: Multiplier-based system that scales across breakpoints
- **Breakpoints**: 
  - Desktop (â‰¥992px)
  - Tablet (768-991px)
  - Large Phone (481-767px)
  - Small Phone (381-480px)
  - Tiny Phone (â‰¤380px)

