## ğŸš€ Deployment

### Deploy to Vercel (Recommended)

1. Push this repository to GitHub
2. Visit [vercel.com](https://vercel.com)
3. Click "New Project"
4. Import your GitHub repository
5. Vercel will automatically detect the configuration
6. Click "Deploy"

### Manual Deployment

You can host this site on any static hosting service:

- **Netlify**: Drag and drop the folder
- **GitHub Pages**: Enable in repository settings
- **Cloudflare Pages**: Connect your repository

## ğŸ”§ Local Development

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/capeblue-pool-care.git
cd capeblue-pool-care
```

2. Open with a local server:
```bash
# Using Python
python -m http.server 8000

# Using Node.js
npx serve

# Using PHP
php -S localhost:8000
```

3. Visit `http://localhost:8000` in your browser

## ğŸ“ Customization

### Update Contact Information

Edit the following in `index.html`:

- Phone numbers: Search for `+27 21 555 0123` and `+27 82 555 0123`
- Email: Replace `info@capebluepool.co.za`
- WhatsApp: Update `https://wa.me/27825550123`

### Change Colors

Modify CSS variables in `assets/css/style.css`:

```css
:root {
  --cb-primary-600: #0F6CA8;
  --cb-primary-500: #1780C4;
  /* ... etc */
}
```

### Add Images

Place images in `assets/images/` and update references in HTML files.

